often select something visually and

4
00:00:07.660 --> 00:00:08.240
you want to play with it.

5
00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:10.430
You want to see what API's
are available on it, or whatever.

6
00:00:10.430 --> 00:00:11.880
So open up the dev tools,

7
00:00:11.880 --> 00:00:15.690
go to the Elements panel,
select any element that you want.

8
00:00:15.690 --> 00:00:19.630
And then you can either go
to the console manually or

9
00:00:19.630 --> 00:00:21.940
you can hit escape to open
up the console drawer.

10
