Just for visibility I will
go to the console manually.

11
00:00:24.490 --> 00:00:28.090
So with nav selected I go to the console,
I hit dollar zeros.

12
00:00:28.090 --> 00:00:32.130
That's my currently selected item and
that brings up the nav in here.

13
00:00:32.130 --> 00:00:34.500
And it goes a few numbers back,
I think maybe three.

14
00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:38.600
So if I go back to elements I
select a new element wrapper.

15
00:00:38.600 --> 00:00:45.178
I go back to console, dollar zero will
be wrapper, but dollar one is still nav.

16
00:00:45.178 --> 00:00:50.020
And so this is kind of a way that you can
just, the thing that you want to do is

17
00:00:50.020 --> 00:00:52.420
bring something into the console and
call something on it, right?

18
00:00:52.420 --> 00:00:58.270
Call add class on it, or get element
by ID, or something like that on it.

19
00:00:58.270 --> 00:01:01.841
